author: Rick Cantu
title: Vandegrift-Vista Ridge will be this week’s game of the year
text:
If Vegas set an over/under line for the Vista Ridge-Vandegrift football game Friday, 100 combined points might be a good starting point.
Last season, Vista Ridge posted a 56-52 victory in double overtime, and the majority of the offensive standouts who played in that game are back this fall.
